360374177353938&type=3&theater)',0,2,'',84,8),(1,'2017-12-17','Christmas show','As we all get into the Christmas spirit we would like to invite all of our students and their guests to our annual Christmas Show!!! On Sunday, December 17, 2017, we would like to see everyone at our studio located at 354 Lakeshore Road West, Mississauga. The show will begin at 5:00 p.m., followed by a visit from Santa Clause and cake!!! Please RSVP with your coaches by no later then December 14, 2017!',1,0,'',0,9),(1,'2017-11-02','HALLOWEEN PARTY!!!','Dear Ghost and Goblins, Our studio welcomes you to our annual Halloween Madness on November 2, 2017. Please arrive in costume at 6:00 p.m. Lots of treats, games and prizes await you. Don\'t forget your dancing shoes as this will be the perfect opportunity for you to demonstrate your skills before our studio\'s big competition on November 12, 2017. See you there!',0,1,'',0,10),(1,'2017-11-12','Mississauga Open Dance Festival 2017','We are very excited to welcome everyone who loves to dance! This competition is for all ages and levels! Enjoy the Art of Dance with us. The event will take place at studio, The Art Of Soul Dance School, located at 354 Lakeshore Road West, Mississauga. Book your calendar from 10:00 am until 3:00 pm. ***Parking is available behind the studio and at the Shoppers Plaza across the street. \r\nShowMiscPicture(Mississauga Open 2017 - poster 3.jpg,2016 Christmas Wonderland by Art of Soul Dance School)\r\n',0,1,'We are very excited to welcome everyone who loves to dance! This competition is for all ages and levels! Enjoy the Art of Dance with us. The event will take place at studio, The Art Of Soul Dance School, located at 354 Lakeshore Road West, Mississauga. Book your calendar from 10:00 am until 3:00 pm.\r\nShowMiscPicture(Mississauga Open 2017 - poster 3.jpg, Art of Soul Dance School)',0,11);
